    {
      "title": "Cost Reference",
      "description": "GCP pricing reference for cost estimation.",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 24 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### GCP Cost Drivers\n| Resource | Unit Cost | Metric to Watch |\n|---|---|---|\n| Dataflow vCPU | ~$0.069/hr | `current_num_vcpus` |\n| Dataflow RAM (GB) | ~$0.003/hr | `current_memory_usage` |\n| Cloud Run | ~$0.000024/instance-sec (1 vCPU) | `instance_count` |\n| Pub/Sub | $0.04/million messages | `send_message_operation_count` |\n| Bigtable reads | $0.26/million | `fetch_success` counter |\n| Bigtable writes | $0.26/million | `rows_written` counter |\n| BQ streaming inserts | $0.01/200 MB | BQ built-in metrics |\n\n### Estimation\n```\nDaily Dataflow cost ≈ avg_vcpus × $0.069 × 24\nDaily prediction cost ≈ daily_dataflow + daily_cloud_run + daily_pubsub + daily_bigtable\nCost per prediction ≈ daily_cost / daily_predictions\n```"
      }
    }
